This is an unofficial third-party Electron wrapper for the Perplexity web
app (https://www.perplexity.ai). It is not endorsed by or affiliated with
Perplexity AI, Inc. "Perplexity" and the Perplexity logo are trademarks of
Perplexity AI, Inc.

This project bundles no Perplexity code or assets other than the icon in
assets/icon-source.png, which is a rendering of Perplexity's own publicly served
favicon. It only loads the Perplexity web app in an Electron window at
runtime. Your use of Perplexity remains subject to Perplexity's own Terms
of Service.
